I should be interested to hear the hon. Gentleman's comments on certain items in the trust. The integrity of the trust is determined by whether those items are maintained. The hon. Gentleman speaks about flotation as though that is likly to go against the interests of the trust. Item A states:
Reuters shall at no time pass into the hands of any one interest, group or faction;
The likely effect of flotation is to extend ownership, not concentrate it—
